 《黑道圣徒》编剧德鲁·霍姆斯出任《孤岛惊魂》IP 总监https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/saints-row-writer-drew-holmes-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-3482539?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=saints-row-writer-德鲁·福尔摩斯成为《孤岛惊魂》IP 导演Imogen DonovanMon, 14 Aug 2023 11:03:26 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3482539 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他说“有大事等待”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/saints-row-writer-drew-holmes-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-3482539">《黑道圣徒》编剧德鲁·霍姆斯出任《孤岛惊魂》IP 总监的</a>消息首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/saints-row"><em>《黑道圣徒》</em></a>编剧德鲁·霍姆斯七年前被<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ubisoft-montreal">育碧蒙特利尔</a>公司聘用，现在担任<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/far-cry">《孤岛惊魂》</a>的 IP 总监。</em></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/say-what-you-like-about-far-cry-6-but-theres-some-real-historical-authenticity-in-its-music-3059031">说说你对《孤岛惊魂 6》的喜爱程度，但它的音乐中有一些真正的历史真实性</a></strong></li></ul><p>霍姆斯在 LinkedIn 上<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7095498948940849152/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">分享了这一消息</a>，并承诺第一人称射击游戏系列将有“重大成果”。在加拿大工作室工作期间，他曾担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/far-cry-5"><em>《孤岛惊魂 5》</em></a>的首席编剧，随后又参与了可下载扩展包<em>《火星失落》</em>的创作。此后，福尔摩斯担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/far-cry-new-dawn"><em>《孤岛惊魂：新黎明》</em></a>的首席编剧，该衍生作品以 2018 年游戏结尾的核爆炸为背景。</p><p> 2006 年，Holmes 开始担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/deep-silver-volition">Deep Silver Volition</a>的质量保证团队成员和写作实习生，不到一年后就晋升为写作团队。 Per <em><a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/writer-of-the-best-saints-row-games-is-now-ip-director-of-far-cry/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PC Gamer</a></em>为<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/saints-row-2">《黑道圣徒 2》</a>编写了环境 NPC 对话、广播电台脚本以及主要和杂项任务对话。</em></p><p> 2011年，他在史蒂夫·贾罗斯的领导下，与杰弗里·比拉夫斯基、卢克·布莱兹和杰西卡·索恩共同创作了《黑道圣徒<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/saints-row-the-third"><em>：第三部》</em></a> 。该条目因其核心活动以及对 Steelport 其他公民的刻画而受到称赞，尤其因其对视频游戏比喻的认识和强调而受到称赞。 </p><figure id="attachment_3482584" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3482584" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3482584" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/saints-row-writer-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3482584" class="wp-caption-text"> 《黑道圣徒：第三重制版》图片来源：Deep Silver</figcaption></figure><p>福尔摩斯曾参与<em>《红色派系》</em>系列、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/bioshock-infinite"><em>《生化奇兵：无限》</em></a>及其资料片<em>《海葬》</em>以及被取消的<em>《黑道圣徒 4》</em> 。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/far-cry-6-review-3063583"><em>《NME</em> 》</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/far-cry-6-review-3063583">对<em>《孤岛惊魂 6》</em>的四星评论</a>中，杰克·塔克批评这款游戏回避了讲述故事的机会。完全实现的政治故事。</p><p> “如果您希望 2021 年的大型动作游戏故事情节轻松，并包含一条穿着背心的鳄鱼和一只毫无冷漠的朋克摇滚公鸡，那么您来对地方了，”杰克解释道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/metal-band-tesseract-launch-vr-game-war-of-being-3482471"><em>《存在之战》</em>是一款由三人开发团队开发的科幻冒险游戏</a>，首席导演兼设计师是金属乐队 TesseracT 的丹尼尔·汤普金斯 (Daniel Tompkins)。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/saints-row-writer-drew-holmes-becomes-far-cry-ip-director-3482539">《黑道圣徒》编剧德鲁·霍姆斯出任《孤岛惊魂》IP 总监的</a>消息首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
